Vernitron Corp said it has set anew record date of July 10 for shareholders entitled to vote onthe proposed merger of Vernitron with &lt;SB Holding Corp>.    The original record date was May 26.    Vernitron said that it currently expects the specialshareholder meeting concerning the merger will be held inAugust.    Following its tender offer in November 1986, SB Holdingholds 55.2 pct of Vernitron, a maker of electromechanicalcomponents and related products and services. Reuter&#3;